# A little quiz with a score. Answers are text - type them exactly.

ask "Which planet is known as the red planet?" into a1
ask "What is the capital of South Africa's Western Cape?" into a2

set score to 0

if a1 is "Mars"
    increase score by 1
    say "Correct!"
else
    say "It was Mars."
end if

if a2 is "Cape Town"
    increase score by 1
    say "Correct!"
else
    say "It was Cape Town."
end if

say "You scored " plus score plus " out of 2"
